{"tid":224861,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"緬甸5日4夜微笑之旅[整合]","createTime":"2017-05-01T11:14:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-03T18:31:21.000Z","uid":53331,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8faa4cff70038375c4bdb26a597eeb55ef9a2142","tid":224861,"uid":53331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T11:14:35.000Z","msg":"今次3人行，主要玩蒲甘。第一次開遊記，低質請包融<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成個行程都好即慶，有一日當講笑咁講就已經成行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇特別plan過隨心所慾，剩係租左酒店同訂夜車。<br />\n<br />\n3人行總共帶左360 USD. 即 16000 Jet, 當地貨幣MMK 當地人讀Jet<br />\n1USD：1350 MMK<br />\n<br />\n基本洗費如下：每人計<br />\n仰光機場 &gt; 唐人街  8000<br />\n唐人街 &gt; JJ夜巴站  10000 夜巴25USD 單程 33750 Jet (我就上網訂左先)<br />\n入蒲甘 25000 <br />\n入蒲甘後去酒店 8000<br />\n租電動單車 7000x1 租左3日21000<br />\n酒店去蒲甘夜巴上車點 8000<br />\n<br />\n總結：<br />\n<br />\n緬甸嘅人好nice好肯幫人。呢個確確實實係一個微笑國家 <br />\n自問都成日飛，去過好多地方，但比我嘅感覺係排外。唔多唔小點都有。<br />\n但來到緬甸，冇呢種感覺，所以人都好nice好肯幫旅客，會成日對旅客微笑 feel到係真心微笑 雖然呢度窮 但好安全，雖然呢度落後 但人民生活幸福，雖然呢度好神秘 但當地人願意慢慢同你分享呢份神秘，我個人好鐘意呢度。<br />\n<br />\n隨著一個國家嘅開放、改革。好快緬甸都已經唔會在係帶住一份神秘，而係同世界開始接軌嘅石屎金錢世界。我真心推薦 要去好快啲去<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蒲甘（緬甸語：ပုဂံ，緬甸語委轉寫：pu.gam，IPA：[bəɡ&agrave;ɴ]）是緬甸曼德勒省的一個具有悠久歷史的地方。從9世紀到13世紀，蒲甘有一個蒲甘王國，該地形成統一的一個地區，後來構成現代緬甸。11世紀和13世紀之間，超過10,000個上座部佛教寺廟矗立於此，寶塔和寺院建於蒲甘平原，2200年歷史的寺廟和佛塔依然完好至今。蒲甘是緬甸重要的旅遊城市。"},{"pid":"56a3977b03d5243ff27e330a9da9d72ad3d57c61","tid":224861,"uid":31618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T11:16:24.000Z","msg":"想去 lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cba3ebe91e47efc35f07e063f525e9189e1760b8","tid":224861,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T11:18:07.000Z","msg":"去過十幾個國家 無咩feel到排外😂"},{"pid":"25da744cdc6e03fb24dcc5c3fed864dd039024c5","tid":224861,"uid":53331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T11:35:54.000Z","msg":"Day 1<br />\n<br />\n香港飛緬甸大約2小時10分鐘，到達後入境，緬甸機場外表睇落好樣衰，係當地人比較中意既平房設計。緬甸同香港有1.5小時時差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實緬甸雖然近幾年先完全開放，但由於仰光曾經作為首都，發展比預期好，來到之後比我預期更加城市化，重靚過中國。<br />\n<br />\n入境緬甸後我地先去兌緬幣。當地好似讀jet 呢度比較有趣 就係唔同面值個率都唔一樣，有幾間唔同公司個價都唔同但就只差幾十jet 。5日4夜行程我地一共兌左360美金。大約46萬jet。<br />\n<br />\n兌完錢就去搵的士，途中見到貢茶 點解會開到周圍都有 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 緬甸奶茶好岀名 幾好飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，一定要試下！機場有個的士櫃位，專門係幫遊客劃實個價唔洗比人湯 ，我地劃價果陣有個香港人埋來問可唔可以join埋，最後4人由機場去唐人街9000jet 大約30分鐘 。<br />\n<br />\n到達唐人街之後大約9:30am..而夜巴要8am先有。所以要係仰光HEA 10個鐘！ 其實我個人覺得仰光冇乜野玩，都冇無聊，可能係因為城市化.. 我地3人鳩finfin咁亂咁行搵下野食。<br />\n<br />\n仰光睇落同大陸有幾分相似，一樣亂鳩咁來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f84qczH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff84qczH.jpg&h=f17de12d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當地人有種特技，就係會將D又大又重既野放係頭度但又可以行得好快都唔會跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w0N7p2Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw0N7p2Z.jpg&h=370ef8c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4XY75pW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4XY75pW.jpg&h=3554d51f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qf14hP4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqf14hP4.jpg&h=2a12f9e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當地人都係鐘意係街邊放D檯檯凳凳就咁坐度食野<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s4vR3cy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs4vR3cy.jpg&h=bae0ebef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/273L89N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F273L89N.jpg&h=1f48d4f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好多蕉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r55iyHz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr55iyHz.jpg&h=b17cf6b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢碗垃圾係我地到緬甸既第一餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我冇食到你都冇睇錯,,係得3粒排骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  4500Jet. 中國人生意模式去到邊都係不變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9gs0a2x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9gs0a2x.jpg&h=1957c60d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇睇下. 發現緬甸好多日本車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有趣既係緬甸冇分左右軑. 因為兩種都見過同搭過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W9A9E9L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW9A9E9L.jpg&h=eb46d18b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢度係Market, 都幾多野睇, 但熱到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好焗<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w501eZ4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw501eZ4.jpg&h=ecb208e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢度係我第一間見過既商場. 都係最後一間見過既商場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽聞緬甸好似得一間商場唔知係咪<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j2H57Q7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj2H57Q7.jpg&h=632d094e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好多雀<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3WhL20d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3WhL20d.jpg&h=126a49d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仰光比較出名既建築<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zc91278.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZc91278.jpg&h=03a13cd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Ev4849.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Ev4849.jpg&h=31232a5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/07fLzx8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F07fLzx8.jpg&h=6367658f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n值得一提既&quot;緬甸雞&quot; 係我見過以來最搞笑既雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小弟不才一直以為雞啼剩係會係早上出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 緬甸雞係全日不亂鳩啼。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ET60688.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FET60688.jpg&h=2cc57026&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去下寺廟周圍行下終於Hea到4pm.. 寺廟冇影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ..熱到仆街,見到間有冷氣既餐廳即刻厹衝入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n塊牛扒幾好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 職員推薦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KPkM7q3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKPkM7q3.jpg&h=701cc912&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n飲飽食醉就開始歷時9小時既夜巴之旅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  舒服得來又辛苦，辛苦得來又慶幸，呢一程夜車真係難以形容係咩感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cc0076c07a1491677a34ac3e59dabfc55457e28","tid":224861,"uid":53331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T11:38:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n值得一提既&quot;緬甸雞&quot; 係我見過以來最搞笑既雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小弟不才一直以為雞啼剩係會係早上出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 緬甸雞係全日不<del>亂</del>段鳩啼。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ET60688.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FET60688.jpg&h=2cc57026&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n</blockquote>"},{"pid":"ad6341a6c5f58246f498f50d32b67fc12487e6e6","tid":224861,"uid":53331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T12:00:40.000Z","msg":"Day 2<br />\n<br />\n經歷左9個鐘夜巴既洗禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  冇錯. 係洗禮. 終於到達旅程既開始：蒲甘.. 5am<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一落車張相影到我手都震鳩埋<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/091d99x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F091d99x.jpg&h=78c4dd24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n餓到仆街. 見到有間唔知乜野厹衝過去食左先算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b6nC7xU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb6nC7xU.jpg&h=cdca0878&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m833k1Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm833k1Z.jpg&h=35777819&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n放心，係有英文餐牌既。我就叫左碗蛋麵. 都幾好食<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Gm8N2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Gm8N2e.jpg&h=7e1cf463&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食完個早餐, 都差唔多日出, 蒲甘日出日落係世界聞名. 現場睇真係好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可惜我影相技術有待改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aR5Sh3T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaR5Sh3T.jpg&h=448ce723&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hf9Vx73.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhf9Vx73.jpg&h=f92b075f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當地奇人奇事真係特別多，繼&quot;緬甸雞&quot;後，在有好鐘意坐車頂, 成日見到D車入面係冇人坐,但車頂係坐滿曬人。只要架車坐得入，人數絕不是問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7EsRRx6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7EsRRx6.jpg&h=fd3922b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0iX8SF5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0iX8SF5.jpg&h=ed56bcae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/19rAWRs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F19rAWRs.jpg&h=198f4d2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去到酒店,呢邊酒店幾好. 我地8am左右到酒店, 職員話可以比5USD提早check in<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/238Re6f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F238Re6f.jpg&h=eb234e6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PNDDRW8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPNDDRW8.jpg&h=9dd036be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NsN18vc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNsN18vc.jpg&h=4eed291a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\ncheck in完梗係拿拿林去租來到蒲甘必玩既ebike！ 係一款電動單車, 唔需要車牌，時遠最高60Km(聲稱) 電池可用8/hr(都係聲稱). 租一日7000 Jet. 來到一定唔可以錯過！因為真係好方便 邊度都去得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wanUa26.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwanUa26.jpg&h=bcb3bd16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n跟住全日就渣住架野周圍飛周圍走去睇下塔咁. 當地好小車. 路大, 所以都可以幾放心。 講就講係路, 來到緬甸, 有一句座右銘 地上本沒路 路是人走出來的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  只要你覺得可以行 佢就係路！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9mw6V93.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9mw6V93.jpg&h=b4368830&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4C0az07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4C0az07.jpg&h=22a27209&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X97Txb4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX97Txb4.jpg&h=ff5ac650&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rB0VH82.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrB0VH82.jpg&h=d820b72d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LHGPksC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLHGPksC.jpg&h=a202d600&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zxz6obo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzxz6obo.jpg&h=d801deed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5QqXRB8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5QqXRB8.jpg&h=c8e8b433&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GZm1y96.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGZm1y96.jpg&h=d66ac3a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NdK1LGh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNdK1LGh.jpg&h=84b813ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當地奇趣又來啦. 繼&quot;緬甸雞&quot;、車頂人之後又一力作... 牛車<br />\n載人既馬車就見得多啦.. 載人既牛車你又見過未呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/75WMT6z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F75WMT6z.jpg&h=0488f1c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/the6A1c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fthe6A1c.jpg&h=94f504a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n年少無知. 未知世間險惡既我地不顧一切好勇咁除鞋諗住上塔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你老母躂地辣撚到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7o9NZ20.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7o9NZ20.jpg&h=94a4c613&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nhY9n62.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnhY9n62.jpg&h=e110abdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDay 2完.. Day 3凌晨會渣住架ebike夜中奔馳去睇第1次日出"},{"pid":"22dbda568473b28b427b00f30fa85d8bf92ce06e","tid":224861,"uid":53331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T12:15:55.000Z","msg":"Day 3<br />\n<br />\n蒲甘貴為日出日落美麗之最，來到又點可以唔睇呢。<br />\n4:30am起身, 前一晚要同租ebike果邊傾定. 如果唔係人地唔會咁早開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢地都好好人, 特登起身就係為左推幾架車比我睇日出。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y4jqF1O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY4jqF1O.jpg&h=bcb97dd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9g6nXj6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9g6nXj6.jpg&h=fa246a8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N5O80uC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN5O80uC.jpg&h=60410be1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5zm11n7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5zm11n7.jpg&h=39e194cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/71nxbvV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F71nxbvV.jpg&h=012af6f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/joQzjk8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjoQzjk8.jpg&h=d75f311d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/359253S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F359253S.jpg&h=2316348d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7nCjb1p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7nCjb1p.jpg&h=da3eb6b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NT4q2nx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNT4q2nx.jpg&h=b93e4910&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/412jxp8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F412jxp8.jpg&h=3457638b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n登上塔頂，萬塔之城盡收眼底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y4jqF1O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY4jqF1O.jpg&h=bcb97dd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇完日出, 返酒店食個早餐訓多陣在渣架車周圍睇下塔咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A72StU1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA72StU1.jpg&h=644c28ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/41mv22q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F41mv22q.jpg&h=917a95d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇完日出又點少得日落？ 不過今日天公不做美. 日落前橫風橫兩. 因為蒲甘好多沙地, 大風起上來D沙會吹入眼。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0bV86w9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0bV86w9.jpg&h=ba85def9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9O6u90g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9O6u90g.jpg&h=de5be665&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TC6cr8v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTC6cr8v.jpg&h=5416c19e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係蒲甘爬塔真係好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人矮D都爬唔到<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gc3299C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGc3299C.jpg&h=60245325&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDay 3完. Day 4會講下蒲甘最美既日落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5a48fe82c985c68c2d3439d59e0ecaf4e2b81bf","tid":224861,"uid":82715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T15:47:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"38edac2f4058db212d64b7e8022d014ac7a0e452","tid":224861,"uid":82715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T15:50:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"652ea6ad88eccf90546b5b874d79ee3d6375cffd","tid":224861,"uid":107488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T01:19:53.000Z","msg":"留名，本身今個月去，點知有突發事去唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4603a27cd7817cacaa06ab7b2ab753cd2aede885","tid":224861,"uid":33777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T02:33:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fce94f54905b0d9e472a131d889b3834083e8800","tid":224861,"uid":19776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T02:44:11.000Z","msg":"LM想今年去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n爸打有冇去睇長頸族同烏本橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8825d3f928f4d5086202ba5f1f94770b2eeb1756","tid":224861,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T12:12:31.000Z","msg":"支"},{"pid":"2b8d31947c62865a184566786829c45e7940a771","tid":224861,"uid":62264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T15:08:11.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 緬甸雞笑撚死我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"936a7ea1e81053aad1859ba0065ac69a3c0770af","tid":224861,"uid":357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T18:31:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}